# docker/snippets/uv/.netrc
#
# Credentials for private PyPI indexes used during Docker image builds.
# UV reads this file natively for authentication when resolving packages.
#
# Copy this file to docker/snippets/uv/.netrc and fill in your credentials.
# The .gitignore in this directory ensures it is never committed.
#
# The default path is docker/snippets/uv/.netrc (repo root relative).
# Override with:
#   export DATAHUB_NETRC_PATH=/path/to/.netrc
#
# One "machine" entry per index host. The host must match the hostname in the
# index URL — do not include the path, port, or scheme.
#
# Format:
#   machine <hostname> login <username> password <token-or-password>
#
# Examples:
machine dl.cloudsmith.io      login <your-cloudsmith-username> password <your-cloudsmith-api-key>
machine cgr.dev               login <your-user> password <your-chainguard-token>
machine my-nexus.example.com  login <user>     password <password>
